	(gr_text "first of all id like to say thank you to my mom none of this would be possible without you thank you for\ngiving birth to me okay birth okay childbirth thanks mom and thanks to my little brother who did nothing\nbut yell at me when i was making my case and also called it ugly thanks bro. thank you to ruj who bravely\nstayed up past his british bedtime to britishly help me make my case and thank you to fallout for funding\nmy broke asse back to motherland and thank you to fallout review team you guys are the goats and shoutout\nto collegeboard for releasing ap scores during fallout to ruin my mood. if i get a 2 everyone at fallout\nowes me ice cream. thank you to celina for being my only motivation to keep going, every time i feel like\nbeing a bum its like. WWCD yk? thank you to all the mandem for making fallout-uk my second home. every single\nday i wish i was british just coz of u guys. shoutout to all fallout orgs you guys rock, fallout is cool asf\nthank you to slack coz i would be in a deep dark place without slack, although i dont love the\ncreeps you bring with it but thanks anyway, slack and also thank you to my dumbass for bringing airpods\nto chicago, losing them there, the goat fanglin xu with the first leg hauling its ass to new york and kat\nwang with the assist from new york to ottawa. shoutout to you 2 . shoutout to axe for replying to my thread\non slack and asking for a shoutout. here you go buddy. shoutout to my cousin for graduating and finishing\ngaokao im excited to go on a trip with you and gramps and although you cant read english just appreciate\nthe sentiment kk ? shoutout to all my kiddos back in fujian love you guys eternally and you guys are the\ncutest and i cant wait to see you again this summer! ykw thank you AGAIN to celina ur goated as FUCK theres\nno way i couldve done this without you actually so you get 2 whole shoutouts. shoutout to lina for saying i \nhave w shoutouts, NO thank you to soup for always rushing and nagging me to do my work. frick you soup >:(\nshoutout to whoever invented diet coke i owe you my life, my firstborn, one of my kidneys (you pick) and\na big shoutout to lookout i am a devout follower. shoutout to the big zrl for making hack club you rock\nthank you to whoever on kicad dev team made front and back silkscreen i owe you... something. its a nice\nfeature so i can give double the shoutouts. thank you to kuro games i cant wait to visit your hq i love you\nso much and i love wuwa and i love carlotta especially and denia and aemeath and shorekeeper i love you kuro\nand finally, last but not least, shoutout to the JLCPCB engineer whos reading all this rn, u da real pcb."
		(at 94.727 85.6516 270)
		(layer "B.SilkS")
		(uuid "af5c7a48-6423-454e-8dc1-2b6383d75ee8")
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1 1)
				(thickness 0.15)
			)
			(justify bottom mirror)
		)
	)
